  <metadata>
    <name>Tour 16: Titisee &amp; Southern Black Forest</name>
    <desc>The longest tour in the collection reaches deep into the southern Black Forest to the iconic Titisee lake via scenic forest roads, returning through the dramatic Höllental (Hell Valley). A full-day adventure through the most dramatic Black Forest landscapes.</desc>
    <author>
      <name>Hockenheim Motorcycle Tours</name>
    </author>
  </metadata>
  <wpt lat="49.322000" lon="8.548000">
